### Customer Similarity

#### Instruction to run

1. To run this, postgres need to be installed on host system.
2. Once postgress installed, configurations of database like database name, user, password, host need to be stored in file called localsettings.py. This repository does not contain this file but need to be created in root directory of the project.
3. Create conda environement and install requirements using `conda env create -f environment.yml` command
4. CSV files of the projects need to be placed under `data/data_files_ml_engineer` path
5. Run app.py. Server might take few minutes to start as the initial distance calculation will be executed.
6. use `find-similar-users/<user-handle>` endpoint to find similar users.